parameters.name: ExcelFile
parameters.description: Path and Microsoft Excel file name to which to export the pattern table; valid filename extensions are .xls , .xlsx , and .xlsm

title: IDimPatternFeatureData.ExportToExcel
description: Exports the pattern table to the specified Microsoft Excel file for this variable pattern feature.
signature:
System.Int32 ExportToExcel( 
   System.String
ExcelFile
,
   System.Boolean
Overwrite
)

parameters.name: ExcelFile
parameters.description: Path and Microsoft Excel file name to which to export the pattern table; valid filename extensions are .xls , .xlsx , and .xlsm

parameters.description: True to overwrite a file in the specified path with the same file name, false to not
